snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP SUES AMBER HEARD AND FIGHTS TO PROVE HIS INNNOCENCE || Court Documents And More
snippet.description:
Hi there everyone, 

It's been a while. But I wanted to do an up to date video regarding whats happening from the publics perspective in Johnny Depp's libel lawsuit against The Sun, and discuss the whopping $50 million dollar lawsuit he's filed against Amber Heard for defamation. (rightfully so) 

As always, screen shots of documents/articles are in the video. Facts clearly stated. 

Important links you'll need: 

Full printed out document that I have in this video, is included in this link from TMZ: https://www.tmz.com/2019/01/22/johnny-depp-amber-heard-beat-strike-lawsuit-sun/

Amber Heard Girl Gaze PSA:https://www.refinery29.com/en-gb/2016/11/131068/amber-heard-domestic-violence-psa

Amber Heard Article for Washington Post, "I spoke out against sexual violence and faced our cultures wrath" -https://www.washingtonpost.com/gdpr-consent/?destination=%2fopinions%2five-seen-how-institutions-protect-men-accused-of-abuse-heres-what-we-can-do%2f2018%2f12%2f18%2f71fd876a-02ed-11e9-b5df-5d3874f1ac36_story.html%3f&utm_term=.c96f551e5419

Amber Heard article for Allure Magazine titled "Why Amber Heard Said She Was So Wrong... Just So Fucking Wrong" https://www.allure.com/story/amber-heard-cover-story-december-2017

Amber Heard UN psa "standing up for domestic violence" -https://twitter.com/un_women/status/1069736812107706368?lang=en-gb

Amber Heard Reads Open Letter About "Johnny Depp Abuse Allegations" at #MeToo Anniversary Event - https://variety.com/2018/scene/news/amber-heard-johnny-depp-open-letter-me-too-1202975127/

The Sun Fails In Bid To Halt Johnny Depp's Libel Action Over Wife Beater Claim - https://www.pressgazette.co.uk/sun-fails-in-bid-to-halt-johnny-depp-libel-action-over-wife-beater-claim/

Johnny Depp Files $50,000,000 Defamation Lawsuit Against Amber Heard, Calls Her Abuse Claims An Elaborate Hoax (Court Documents included)- https://theblast.com/johnny-depp-amber-heard-defamation-lawsuit/

Johnny Depp Claims Amber Heard Started Improper RelationShip With Elon Musk 1 Month After Marriage: https://theblast.com/johnny-depp-amber-heard-elon-musk-relationship/ (Court Document from previous article is discussed further in this one.)

I apologise that it's a long video, but there was alot to go over. 

Thank you for watching, Keep fighting the good fight. 

AOV x
